  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package carries a subtle W-EP-03 weakness: the primary experimental dataset (FDA pump PIV benchmark) was acquired in 2025-Q4, prior to the January 2026 model revision that updated the power-law hemolysis constants and near-wall mesh topology. Re-validation against the refreshed dataset is noted as planned but not yet executed.",
